'''''The Great American Cross-Country Road Race''''' is a racing game published in 1985 by [[Activision]]. 

The game puts the player in the position of a driver of a high-performance car, racing across the United States while passing through its major cities. It is known for having several obstacles that the player must watch out for, such as weather, road conditions, gas refilling, and highway patrol.

